This is wonderful that you shared this with us!<br>
It is refreshing to know of others doing His work for Him.<br>
This is what our book is about.  God came to us and asked us to do the same for Him.  <br>
The writing in our book(s) is what we call: inspirational writing, as it is coming from God.  It is not to be confused with automatic writing, as this can happen too, but usually is associated with people's spirits who have passed on, but not necessarily God.  Sometimes automatic writing has been known to come from other sources that we will not mention here, as we do not like to give any energy thinking about the other sources.  <br>
Inspirational writing, however, is writing that is &quot;inspired&quot; being of God.  You will see many similarities in our books with what Vassula has received.  <br>
God told us we would be hearing of others doing similar work for Him, and it is so exciting to hear this news!<br>
<br>
Thank you again for sharing this beautiful information with the board.  Hopefully others will receive this information with open minds and hearts, and truly understand that God has not stopped communicating with His people in this way!<br>
<br>
Thank you for coming here and please visit often. It sounds like we have a lot we can talk about!<br>
<br>
God Bless you!<br>
Debra <br>
